for every task: when rewritePrompt is true, create a single const rewriter = new
PromptRewriter(this.getOpenAIService()) before iterating over buildTasks, then
inside the for loop call rewriter.rewrite(task.description) and proceed to await
this.jobManager.updateTaskOriginalDescription(task.uuid, result.original) and
assign task.description = result.rewritten; keep the existing try/catch behavior
but remove the in-loop new PromptRewriter(...) call.
```

